strings.Value: {n}Chwurk happily taps his foot as you approach.{/n} "Ah, adventurer friend! You help goblins, Chwurk help you! Bring good wares, trade them for nothing!
{n}The goblin is sincerely surprised by the question.{/n} "Go-go, my cart push-push, come! Or you think Chwurk can fly, uaha-ha-ha?!"
